title: COAST / MORELL barks whirling
description: Morel says this stuff in Whirling.

dialogueTree.title: Morell, the Cryptozoologist: ""It's a bit crowded in here.""
Morell, the Cryptozoologist: ""The evidence is right there -- we..."
dialogueTree.english: "The evidence is right there -- we can't just ignore it."
dialogueTree.polish: „Dowody mamy jak na dłoni. Nie możemy ich zignorować”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Доказы перад намі, як на далоні. Мы не можам іх ігнараваць".

dialogueTree.title: Morell, the Cryptozoologist: ""There was a confirmed sighting in..."
dialogueTree.english: "There was a confirmed sighting in Mirova in December."
dialogueTree.polish: „Potwierdzono, że pojawił się w grudniu w Mirowej”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Пацверджана, што ён з'явіўся ў снежні ў Міровай".

dialogueTree.title: Morell, the Cryptozoologist: ""Hate to break it to you, Gary, but..."
dialogueTree.english: "Hate to break it to you, Gary, but rhinos don't just combust in flames."
dialogueTree.polish: „Przykro mi, że muszę ci to mówić, Gary, ale nosorożce nie ulegają ot tak samozapłonowi”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Мне шкада, што мушу гэта казаць табе, Гары, але насарогі не ўспыхваюць так проста самазапальваннем".

dialogueTree.title: Morell, the Cryptozoologist: ""An *unconfirmed* sighting is just..."
Morell, the Cryptozoologist: ""Are you enjoying yourself, darling?""
Morell, the Cryptozoologist: ""C'mon, Gary, it's never that black..."
dialogueTree.english: "C'mon, Gary, it's never that black and white."
dialogueTree.polish: „Daj spokój, Gary, to nigdy nie jest takie czarno-białe”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Супакойся, Гэри, гэта ніколі не бывае такім чорна-белым".

dialogueTree.title: Morell, the Cryptozoologist: ""God, I hope the traps will hold...""
dialogueTree.english: "God, I hope the traps will hold..."
